{"tid":1327612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲議會將辯論香港決議案　促停售「人群管制裝備」","createTime":"2019-07-17T16:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:22:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":142,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ce63468469874206b912006e82bc195eccf61835","tid":1327612,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1468922_1_20190717231850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1468922_1_20190717231850.jpg&h=9ebbe981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會將於當地星期四早上，辯論香港的決議案，將就香港近期就反修例爭議引發的衝突表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n根據歐洲議會的網上公告，列出的決議案議題，包括促請停止向香港出售「人群管制裝備」，是97以來首次，針對香港提出的制裁。另外，亦會強調歐洲議會充分尊重香港特別行政區基本法、一國兩制原則，強調中國政府仍然受《中英聯合聲明》的約束，強烈譴責中方對香港內政不斷加劇干涉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468922-20190717.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468922-20190717.htm&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=d3fca1e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468922-20190717.htm&h=b0a927e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468922-20190717.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4a7bba4d4967651050669e5bff41d95246984231","tid":1327612,"uid":166729,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日口交部又發癲了"},{"pid":"ed56874d2f886b89ae73d679693916e75e765055","tid":1327612,"uid":78947,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"用小米 華為啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國的會。。。"},{"pid":"e0070c305743e9048cb5502cff8e7b351f6a7c0a","tid":1327612,"uid":275865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1